&lt;li&gt;5+ years of hands-on experience designing and developing complex electronic hardware from concept to production&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A passion for hardware development and a desire to work in a dynamic, hands-on environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated ability to design, build, and test hardware from scratch.&lt;/li&gt;
