&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Embedded Software Engineer - Network Software&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a Embedded Software Engineer on the Network Software team at Astranis, you will be responsible for assisting with architecture, high level design choices, development, execution, and implementation of the flight software that commands and monitors the spacecraft. Additionally, you will mentor junior members and collaborate with other teams to ensure that the software you&#39;ve implemented works on their hardware.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role will contribute to both commercial and US Government programs.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
