&lt;li&gt;Work with multiple FPGAs and toolchains&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Interface FPGAs with high speed data converters, memories, MCUs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design, implement and test radiation mitigation schemes on FPGA&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate closely with DSP/radio algorithm designer&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate closely with embedded firmware and software engineers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist in recruiting, interviewing, and hiring additional teammates to our rapidly-growing team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&quot;JobDescriptionFPGAEngineerI/II-Requirements&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Requirements&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
