&lt;li&gt;A passion for hardware development, including working in a fast-paced environment and hands-on design and development&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in designing, implementing, verifying and testing high throughput systems implemented on FPGAs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong proficiency with Verilog (preferably SystemVerilog) for both synthesis and verification&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&quot;JobDescriptionFPGAEngineerI/II-Bonus&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Bonus&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h4&gt;
